          <p class="product-brand">Tom Ford</p>
          <p class="product-price"><span class="old-price">&euro;1.200</span> &euro;840</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-card fade-in" style="--delay: 0.3s">
        <div class="product-image">
          <div class="product-placeholder">
            <div class="product-shape shape-watch"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-overlay">
            <button class="quick-view-btn">Vista Rapida</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-info">
          <h3>Orologio Automatico Oro Rosa</h3>
          <p class="product-brand">Manifattura Italiana</p>
          <p class="product-price">&euro;5.600</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-card fade-in" style="--delay: 0.4s">
        <div class="product-image">
          <div class="product-placeholder">
            <div class="product-shape shape-scarf"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-overlay">
            <button class="quick-view-btn">Vista Rapida</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-info">
          <h3>Foulard in Seta Stampata</h3>
          <p class="product-brand">Valentino</p>
          <p class="product-price">&euro;680</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-card fade-in" style="--delay: 0.5s">
        <div class="product-image">
          <div class="product-placeholder">
            <div class="product-shape shape-sunglasses"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-overlay">
            <button class="quick-view-btn">Vista Rapida</button>
          </div>
          <span class="product-badge">Esclusivo</span>
        </div>
        <div class="product-info">
          <h3>Occhiali da Sole Titanio</h3>
          <p class="product-brand">Zegna</p>
          <p class="product-price">&euro;520</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured banner -->
  <section class="featured fade-in">
    <div class="featured-glass">
      <p class="featured-tag">Edizione Limitata</p>
      <h2 class="featured-title">Capsule Collection<br /><span class="gradient-text">Notte d'Oro</span></h2>
      <p class="featured-desc">Solo 50 pezzi numerati. Ogni articolo viene consegnato in una confezione esclusiva realizzata a mano dai nostri artigiani.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Scopri la Capsule</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="testimonials">
    <div class="section-header fade-in">
      <p class="section-tag">Cosa Dicono i Clienti</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Esperienze <span class="gradient-text">Autentiche</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card fade-in" style="--delay: 0s">
        <div class="testimonial-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"Un servizio impeccabile. La borsa che ho acquistato supera ogni aspettativa. La qualità si percepisce al primo tocco."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">MR</div>
          <div>
            <p class="author-name">Maria Rossi</p>
            <p class="author-role">Milano</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card fade-in" style="--delay: 0.15s">
        <div class="testimonial-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"Ho regalato un orologio della collezione a mio marito. L'emozione che ho visto nei suoi occhi vale più di qualsiasi cifra."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">LB</div>
          <div>
            <p class="author-name">Laura Bianchi</p>
            <p class="author-role">Roma</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card fade-in" style="--delay: 0.3s">
        <div class="testimonial-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"Confezione curata in ogni dettaglio, spedizione velocissima. Un'esperienza di acquisto che ti fa sentire davvero speciale."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">GV</div>
          <div>
            <p class="author-name">Giovanni Verdi</p>
            <p class="author-role">Firenze</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter -->
  <section class="newsletter fade-in">
    <div class="newsletter-glass">
      <h2 class="newsletter-title">Entra nel <span class="gradient-text">Club Esclusivo</span></h2>
      <p class="newsletter-desc">Accesso anticipato alle nuove collezioni, inviti a eventi privati e offerte riservate ai membri.</p>
      <form class="newsletter-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault()">
        <input type="email" placeholder="La tua email" class="newsletter-input" />
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Iscriviti</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3 class="footer-logo gradient-text">LUXE NOIR</h3>
        <p class="footer-tagline">L'arte del lusso accessibile.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Collezioni</h4>
        <a href="#">Donna</a>
        <a href="#">Uomo</a>
        <a href="#">Accessori</a>
        <a href="#">Nuovi Arrivi</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Assistenza</h4>
        <a href="#">Spedizioni</a>
        <a href="#">Resi</a>
        <a href="#">Contatti</a>
        <a href="#">FAQ</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Seguici</h4>
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
        <a href="#">Pinterest</a>
        <a href="#">Facebook</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Luxe Noir. Tutti i diritti riservati. &mdash; Demo template di Marco Munich</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    // Intersection Observer for fade-in
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });

    document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));

    // Animated counters
    const counterObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          const counters = entry.target.querySelectorAll('.stat-number');
          counters.forEach(counter => {
            const target = parseInt(counter.getAttribute('data-target'));
            const duration = 2000;
            const start = performance.now();
            const animate = (now) => {
              const elapsed = now - start;
              const progress = Math.min(elapsed / duration, 1);
              const eased = 1 - Math.pow(1 - progress, 3);
              counter.textContent = Math.floor(target * eased).toLocaleString('it-IT');
              if (progress < 1) requestAnimationFrame(animate);
              else counter.textContent = target.toLocaleString('it-IT');
            };
            requestAnimationFrame(animate);
          });
          counterObserver.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.3 });

    document.querySelectorAll('.stats').forEach(el => counterObserver.observe(el));

    // 3D tilt on product cards
    document.querySelectorAll('.product-card').forEach(card => {
      card.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
        const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
        const x = (e.clientX - rect.left) / rect.width - 0.5;
        const y = (e.clientY - rect.top) / rect.height - 0.5;
        card.style.transform = `perspective(1000px) rotateY(${x * 8}deg) rotateX(${-y * 8}deg) scale(1.02)`;
      });
      card.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
        card.style.transform = 'perspective(1000px) rotateY(0deg) rotateX(0deg) scale(1)';
      });
    });

    // Cart badge bounce on load
    setTimeout(() => {
      document.querySelector('.cart-badge')?.classList.add('bounce');
    }, 1500);
  </script>

  <style>
    /* ========== RESET & BASE ========== */
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0a;
      color: #e8e0d4;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Custom scrollbar */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0a0a0a; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #c9a96e; border-radius: 4px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #dbb878; }

    /* Noise overlay */
    .noise {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 9999; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.03;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      background-repeat: repeat;
    }

    /* Gradient text */
    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e 0%, #f0d89c 40%, #c9a96e 60%, #a67c3d 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    /* Fade-in animation */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
      transition-delay: var(--delay, 0s);
    }
    .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* ========== PARTICLES ========== */
    .particles { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    .dot {
      position: absolute;
      width: 4px; height: 4px;
      background: #c9a96e;
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: 0.15;
      animation: floatDot 20s infinite ease-in-out;
    }
    .dot-1 { top: 10%; left: 15%; animation-delay: 0s; }
    .dot-2 { top: 25%; left: 80%; animation-delay: -3s; width: 6px; height: 6px; }
    .dot-3 { top: 60%; left: 10%; animation-delay: -7s; }
    .dot-4 { top: 70%; left: 70%; animation-delay: -11s; width: 3px; height: 3px; }
    .dot-5 { top: 40%; left: 50%; animation-delay: -5s; width: 5px; height: 5px; }
    .dot-6 { top: 85%; left: 30%; animation-delay: -9s; }
    .dot-7 { top: 15%; left: 60%; animation-delay: -13s; width: 3px; height: 3px; }
    .dot-8 { top: 50%; left: 90%; animation-delay: -2s; }
    @keyframes floatDot {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); opacity: 0.15; }
      25% { transform: translate(30px, -40px) scale(1.5); opacity: 0.3; }
      50% { transform: translate(-20px, -80px) scale(1); opacity: 0.1; }
      75% { transform: translate(40px, -30px) scale(1.3); opacity: 0.25; }
    }

    /* ========== BACK BUTTON ========== */
    .back-btn {
      position: fixed; top: 24px; left: 24px; z-index: 100;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: rgba(10,10,10,0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);
      border-radius: 50px;
      color: #c9a96e;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      background: rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
      border-color: rgba(201,169,110,0.5);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,169,110,0.15);
    }
    .back-arrow { font-size: 1.1rem; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
    .back-btn:hover .back-arrow { transform: translateX(-3px); }

    /* ========== CART ICON ========== */
    .cart-icon {
      position: fixed; top: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 100;
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: rgba(10,10,10,0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: #c9a96e;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cart-icon:hover {
      background: rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
      border-color: rgba(201,169,110,0.5);
    }
    .cart-badge {
      position: absolute; top: -4px; right: -4px;
      width: 20px; height: 20px;
      background: #c9a96e;
      color: #0a0a0a;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .cart-badge.bounce { animation: badgeBounce 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.27, 1.55); }
    @keyframes badgeBounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.4); }
    }

    /* ========== HERO ========== */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      padding: 120px 24px 80px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-gradient {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1207 30%, #0a0a0a 50%, #12090a 70%, #0a0a0a 100%);
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      animation: gradient 15s ease infinite;
    }
    @keyframes gradient {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }
    .hero-content {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 700px;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #c9a96e;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(232,224,212,0.7);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d);
      color: #0a0a0a;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: 50px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(201,169,110,0.3);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      background: transparent;
      color: #c9a96e;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: 50px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.4);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
      border-color: #c9a96e;
    }

    /* Floating mockups */
    .floating-mockups {
      position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .mockup {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(201,169,110,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      animation: floatMockup 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .mockup-1 { width: 180px; height: 220px; top: 15%; left: 8%; animation-delay: 0s; }
    .mockup-2 { width: 140px; height: 180px; top: 20%; right: 10%; animation-delay: -2.5s; }
    .mockup-3 { width: 120px; height: 160px; bottom: 15%; left: 15%; animation-delay: -5s; }
    .mockup-inner {
      width: 60%; height: 40%;
      margin: 25% auto 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,169,110,0.15), rgba(201,169,110,0.05));
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    @keyframes floatMockup {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(2deg); }
    }

    /* ========== MARQUEE ========== */
    .marquee-wrapper {
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 32px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
    }
    .marquee {
      display: flex; gap: 40px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      animation: scrollMarquee 25s linear infinite;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(201,169,110,0.4);
    }
    .sep { color: rgba(201,169,110,0.2); }
    @keyframes scrollMarquee {
      0% { transform: translateX(0); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* ========== STATS ========== */
    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 80px auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-number {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c9a96e;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(232,224,212,0.5);
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ========== PRODUCTS ========== */
    .products { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px; }
    .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
    .section-tag {
      font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #c9a96e; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .product-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .product-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .product-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(201,169,110,0.25);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 0 40px rgba(201,169,110,0.05);
    }
    .product-image {
      position: relative;
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #131313, #1a1a1a);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .product-placeholder {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .product-shape {
      width: 50%; height: 40%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      opacity: 0.15;
    }
    .shape-bag { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d); border-radius: 8px 8px 16px 16px; }
    .shape-jacket { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d); border-radius: 4px; width: 60%; }
    .shape-shoe { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d); border-radius: 50px 50px 8px 8px; width: 55%; height: 25%; }
    .shape-watch { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d); border-radius: 50%; width: 35%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 35%; }
    .shape-scarf { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d); border-radius: 4px; width: 30%; height: 60%; transform: rotate(-15deg); }
    .shape-sunglasses { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d); border-radius: 50px; width: 55%; height: 20%; }

    .product-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(10,10,10,0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    }
    .product-card:hover .product-overlay { opacity: 1; }
    .quick-view-btn {
      padding: 12px 28px;
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid #c9a96e;
      color: #c9a96e;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: 50px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    .product-card:hover .quick-view-btn { transform: translateY(0); }
    .quick-view-btn:hover {
      background: #c9a96e;
      color: #0a0a0a;
    }

    .product-badge {
      position: absolute; top: 16px; left: 16px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      background: #c9a96e;
      color: #0a0a0a;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: 50px;
    }
    .product-badge.sale { background: #b04040; color: #fff; }

    .product-info { padding: 20px; }
    .product-info h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .product-brand {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(201,169,110,0.6);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .product-price {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #c9a96e;
    }
    .old-price {
      text-decoration: line-through;
      color: rgba(232,224,212,0.3);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }

    /* ========== FEATURED ========== */
    .featured {
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 40px auto 80px; padding: 0 24px;
    }
    .featured-glass {
      background: rgba(201,169,110,0.04);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 80px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .featured-glass::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: -50%; left: -50%;
      width: 200%; height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 50%, rgba(201,169,110,0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
      animation: featuredGlow 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes featuredGlow {
      0% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      100% { transform: translate(5%, 5%); }
    }
    .featured-tag {
      font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #c9a96e; margin-bottom: 16px; position: relative;
    }
    .featured-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .featured-desc {
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(232,224,212,0.6);
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto 32px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* ========== TESTIMONIALS ========== */
    .testimonials { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px; }
    .testimonial-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    .testimonial-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(201,169,110,0.2);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .testimonial-stars { color: #c9a96e; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .testimonial-text {
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(232,224,212,0.7);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .testimonial-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .author-avatar {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #a67c3d);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: #0a0a0a;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .author-name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .author-role { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.4); }

    /* ========== NEWSLETTER ========== */
    .newsletter { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 80px; padding: 0 24px; }
    .newsletter-glass {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .newsletter-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .newsletter-desc {
      font-weight: 300; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.6);
      margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .newsletter-form {
      display: flex; gap: 12px; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .newsletter-input {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15);
      border-radius: 50px;
      color: #e8e0d4;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .newsletter-input::placeholder { color: rgba(232,224,212,0.3); }
    .newsletter-input:focus { border-color: #c9a96e; }

    /* ========== FOOTER ========== */
    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
      padding: 60px 24px 32px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .footer-tagline { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.4); }
    .footer-col h4 {
      font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #c9a96e; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .footer-col a {
      display: block; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.5);
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px; transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: #c9a96e; }
    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.06);
      padding-top: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-bottom p { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.3); }

    /* ========== RESPONSIVE ========== */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .product-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .testimonial-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 32px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .product-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 360px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-title { font-size: 2.4rem; }
      .hero-buttons { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
      .newsletter-form { flex-direction: column; }
      .floating-mockups { display: none; }
      .back-btn { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 8px 14px; }
      .featured-glass { padding: 48px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
